description: {"blocks":[{"key":"36cee","text":"This is the protocol for the research of the coverage of DOAJ journals' citations through OpenCitations. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"35bje","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"cblk5","text":"Our goal is to find out:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"enlfq","text":"about the coverage of articles from open access journals in DOAJ journals as citing and cited articles,","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"a7afi","text":"how many citations do DOAJ journals receive and do, and how many of these citations involve open access articles as both citing and cited entities,","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"3nctd","text":"as well as the presence of trends over time of the availability of citations involving articles published in open access journals in DOAJ journals.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"kg0m","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"dq51f","text":"Our research focuses on DOAJ journals exclusively, using OpenCitations as a tool.
